computers and the UPS.  If you go to the site below, you'll find
information on how to cable up the serial port on the UPS.  Once 
you have it hooked up I can install/configure the "apcupsd" daemon
which will perform an orderly shutdown whenever the battery of the UPS 
is below 10%.  (our if you guys want to you can do this...)

